<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-29-0728 </DOCNO><TEXT>This document outlines policies and programs under the Renewable EnergyDivision of Energy, Mines and Resources Canada. Criteria for eligibility,types of assistance available, and examples of recent projects are given.Specific program areas are: alternate energy development for Prince EdwardIsland; bioenergy development, aimed at substituting biomass for non-renewablefuels and chemicals; solar energy development, including small hydroand wind energy, and applications relevant to both domestic and industrial/commercialuses; and a demonstration program for promoting off-oil energy alternativesand conservation options for remote communities.</TEXT></DOC>